   If you like the program and decide to use it, then please spend a few
   minutes writing a message to the @{" author " LINK "Author"}.
   Even a simple sentence like:
   "I use @{B}MiraWizRUN@{UB}. My name is @{i}name surname address@{ui}"
   will be very welcome.

